~ start
if GameState.get_value(GameState.IS_LOCKDOWN_CLEARED) != true
	You press the button. The lockdown is cleared.
	do GameState.set_value(GameState.IS_LOCKDOWN_CLEARED, true)
	do SoundEffects.play_lockdown_disabled_sound()
else
	You press the button. The lockdown is in progress again. Is this what you want?
	do GameState.set_value(GameState.IS_LOCKDOWN_CLEARED, false)
	do SoundEffects.play_lockdown_enabled_sound()
=> END
